the first public version. Then we give the broad outlines of our implementation and show how we took as much advantage as possible of the main features of Scheme. We also explain what we really missed and suggest some ways to improve these points.</p><p><u>Downloads:</u></p><ul><li><a href="http://repository.readscheme.org/ftp/papers/sw2005/hufflen.ps.gz">ps</a></li><li><a href="http://repository.readscheme.org/ftp/papers/sw2005/hufflen.pdf">pdf</a></li></ul><p><u>Bibtex citation:</u></p><pre>@inproceedings{
